com.bluegosling.collections

Class TransformingMap.ValuesOnly<K,VI,VO>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bluegosling.collections.TransformingMap<K,VI,K,VO>
      • com.bluegosling.collections.TransformingMap.ValuesOnly<K,VI,VO>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type of key in the map
    VI - the "input" value type
    VO - the "output" value type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Map<K,VO>
    Enclosing class:
    TransformingMap<KI,VI,KO,VO>

    public static class TransformingMap.ValuesOnly<K,VI,VO>
extends TransformingMap<K,VI,K,VO>
    A TransformingMap that only transforms map values, not keys. Due to this constraint, it provides more efficient implementations for some methods.
